Canvas frames are 100% renewable wood with a matte black enamel finish. The solid wood black floater frame is 1.75” deep.

The framed canvas has been created with precision and care, designed to stand the test of time. 

The product sizes relate to the size of the canvas, please add 1.5” to calculate the overall dimensions including the frame.

Water based inks and local fulfilment from 10 facilities over 6 countries helps reduce carbon into the atmosphere.
